The paper proposes a framework for continual learning for generative models, which involves regularization in the feature space. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), and natural language processing (cs.CL), which are all relevant to generative models. Among these sub-categories, cs.LG is the most likely as it is the primary sub-category for machine learning research.
